    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">It's rush hour at &quot;The Drooling Stein&quot;, the goblins' favorite tavern. A long queue has formed in front of the counter. <br>The bartender, a tired old troll, can only serve one goblin per minute.<br><br>However, goblins are known for their impatience. <br>Each goblin in the queue has a <var>patience</var> level represented by a number of minutes. <br>If a goblin has to wait longer than their <var>patience</var> level, they leave the queue furiously and consume nothing.<br><br>Knowing that the service starts at minute <const>0</const>, determine how many goblins will successfully get their beer before losing their <var>patience</var>.<br><br><strong>Specific Rules</strong><br>- The goblin at the front of the queue is served instantly if his <var>patience</var> hasn't run out.<br>- Serving a goblin takes exactly <const>1</const> minute (which advances the global time by <const>1</const>).<br>- Goblins who lose <var>patience</var> leave the queue, which takes <const>0</const> minutes for the bartender.<br>- The order of the queue does not change (no cutting in line).</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1:</strong> An integer <var>N</var> representing the number of goblins in the queue.<br><strong>Line 2:</strong> <var>N</var> space-separated integers, representing the <var>patience</var> level (in minutes) of each goblin, in the queue's order.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><strong>A single integer:</strong> the total number of goblins who were served.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; <var>N</var> &le; 100<br>0 &le; <var>patience</var> &le; 100</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">5\n0 2 3 1 5</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">4</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
